| Priority | Fix |
|---|---|
| **High** | Add error-handling middleware; don't leak stack traces |
| **High** | `helmet` + disable `x-powered-by` |
| **High** | Body size `limit` on `express.json()` |
| **Medium** | Rate limiting on public endpoints |
| **Medium** | `zod`/`joi` validation for any user-controlled input (query, params, body) |
| **Medium** | `server.listen` error handler + graceful shutdown on SIGTERM/SIGINT |
| **Low** | `PORT` from env, remove PII (email) from unauthenticated responses |

