| Input validation | Validate **every** route param, query, and body with a schema library; reject (don't sanitize-silently) invalid input |
| Error responses | Return generic messages; log details server-side only |
| CORS | Explicit allowlist of origins via `cors({ origin: [...] })` — never `*` for authenticated endpoints |
