| Dependencies | Run `npm audit` in CI; use `npm ci` with a lockfile |
| TLS | Terminate TLS at a reverse proxy (nginx/ALB); set `trust proxy` appropriately |
| Logging | Structured logs with redaction of credentials and PII |

