| Concern | Recommendation |
|---|---|
| **Headers** | Use `helmet()` for CSP, HSTS, `X-Content-Type-Options`, etc. |
| **Fingerprinting** | `app.disable('x-powered-by')`. |
| **Rate limiting** | `express-rate-limit` per-IP, stricter on auth endpoints. |
| **Body size** | `express.json({ limit: '10kb' })` to prevent DoS. |
| **Input validation** | Validate **every** `req.body`, `req.params`, `req.query` with `zod`/`joi`. Reject on failure, don't coerce silently. |
| **Output** | Never return stack traces. Strip PII (e.g., emails) unless authenticated. |
| **Auth** | Add an auth middleware before `/users`. Use short-lived JWTs or signed sessions. |
| **CORS** | Explicit allow-list with the `cors` package; never `*` for credentialed endpoints. |
| **Logging** | Structured logs (`pino`), no secrets, include request ID. |
| **Dependencies** | Run `npm audit` and Dependabot/Renovate. |
| **TLS** | Terminate TLS at a reverse proxy; set `app.set('trust proxy', 1)` when behind one. |
