| No HTTPS / HSTS | Terminate TLS at a reverse proxy, set `trust proxy`, and use `helmet.hsts()` |
| No request logging | `morgan('combined')` piped to a real logger (pino/winston) |
| `console.log` / `console.error` in production | Use a structured logger; never log PII or secrets |

**Example hardened setup:**
