```

### 4. No process-level error handling
Add listeners so uncaught exceptions log and exit cleanly instead of leaving the process in an undefined state:

```js
process.on('unhandledRejection', (reason) => { console.error(reason); process.exit(1); });
process.on('uncaughtException',  (err)    => { console.error(err);    process.exit(1); });
```

