| Injection attacks | `express-validator` + parameterized DB queries |
| Info disclosure via errors | Generic client messages, detailed server logs only |
| Mass assignment / PII leakage | Whitelist response fields (`{ id, name }`), no email |
| Crash-on-error | Centralized error middleware + `unhandledRejection` handler |
| Dropped requests on deploy | `SIGTERM` graceful shutdown |
| Hardcoded config | `process.env.PORT`, `NODE_ENV` |

