### 1. No global error handler
Uncaught errors in route handlers will leak stack traces to clients (Express default behavior in non-production).

### 2. No security headers
Missing `helmet` — responses lack `X-Content-Type-Options`, `Strict-Transport-Security`, `X-Frame-Options`, CSP, etc.

### 3. No rate limiting
